				</h1>
				<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-[#a6adc8] text-lg">
					Senior Data Engineer · PhD in Reinforcement Learning
				</p>
			</div>
			<p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-[#bac2de] text-xl leading-relaxed">
				I design data systems, also fix the leaky pipes 😏
			</p>
			<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-[#a6adc8]">
