							Great Expectations · Python · GitLab CI
						</span>
						<span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-[#89b4fa] text-lg">→</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a
					href="/archive"
					class="group flex flex-col p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-[#313244] hover:border-blue-600 dark:hover:border-[#89b4fa] rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-[#181825] transition-colors h-full"
