						<span class="text-gray-400 dark:text-[#6c7086] hidden sm:inline">—</span>
						<span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-[#bac2de]">Data Engineer</span>
					</div>
					<span class="text-gray-400 dark:text-[#a6adc8] text-sm mt-1 sm:mt-0">
						Mar 2019 – Nov 2019
					</span>
